high_descs: Turn to your left walk towards the fridge turn to your left face the counter
Pick up the ladle on the counter beside the sink
Turn to your left move few steps then turn right
Put the ladle in the sink then rinse it
Turn around to your left, then right face the counter
Open the second lower cabinet from the right then put the ladle inside and close the drawer
anns.task_desc: Put a clean ladle on the cabinet

high_descs: Take a step forward, then turn left and walk over to the fridge, then turn left to face the counter.
Pick up the large golden spoon with a blue handle off of the counter.
Turn left and begin walking towards the oven, then turn right and walk up to the sink.
Put the large golden spoon into the sink basin and turn on the water, after a couple seconds turn the water off and remove the now clean spoon.
Turn around and begin walking forward, then turn back around to face the lower cabinets.
Open the rightmost lower cabinet door below the sink and put the clean golden spoon inside, then close the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean golden spoon into a cabinet.

high_descs: Go left and then turn right and then left at the fridge and go forward to stand at the counter with a big spoon.
Pick the big soon up from the counter.
Move left and turn to face the sink.
Put the spoon in the sink and turn the water on and then off and pick the spoon up out of the sink.
Move to the cabinets to the lower cabinets left of the sink.
Put the spoon in the cabinet on the lower right and shut the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean spoon in the cabinet.
